  SNYK-JS-ELLIPTIC-14908844:
    - '*':
        reason: >-
          No upstream fix (Snyk: "There is no fix"; every published elliptic
          release incl. latest 6.6.1 is in range). Transitive dev/build-only via
          @rsbuild/plugin-node-polyfill › crypto-browserify › create-ecdh ›
          elliptic — bundled into the browser crypto polyfill, never used for
          signature verification with attacker-controlled curve parameters. Not
          reachable. Revisit before expiry or when an elliptic fix ships.
        expires: 2026-10-20T00:00:00.000Z
        created: 2026-07-20T00:00:00.000Z
